    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape, runs super smooth, and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go! I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it or take it for a test drive!",
