    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E92 M3 featuring the iconic S65 4.0L V8 and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is complemented by a variable M-differential lock for optimized lateral dynamics. Essential preventative maintenance\u2014specifically rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service\u2014has been completed. The suspension geometry remains precise, and the chassis is free of subframe fatigue. A driver-quality example with exceptional mechanical integrity and visceral performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
