    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and luxury. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish that catches the light beautifully, showing only the minor, honest signs of road use one would expect from a well-loved car, such as tiny stone chips on the front bumper. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin featuring supple leather seating with minimal creasing and a full suite of functional high-tech amenities, including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, this car is in strong health; it has been serviced regularly at authorized intervals, providing a smooth, responsive, and quiet ride. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and confident. Whether you're navigating city streets or cruising on the highway, this car offers a dependable and premium driving experience. We have comprehensive service records available for your review to ensure complete peace of mind. It\u2019s a turn-key opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with care.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
