    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this beauty won't let you down. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m happy to chat or answer any questions you might have. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
